title: Nikki Glaser
itunes:title: Nikki Glaser
description:
Nikki Glaser is back for a fourth time and this time she and Whitney dissect the Oscars slap heard round the world, the catharsis of The Kardashians, and how to take eight years off your biological age.  Nikki's reality show "WELCOME HOME NIKKI GLASER?" premieres May 1st on E! and check out her podcast NIKKI GLASER POD wherever you get your pods.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
